#################################
            README
##################################

Vendor.js is the file containing all the functions that has been done for now

The html directory contains html files  (index.html, my_products.html, my_account.html, dashboard.html)
Html files are examples of how to use the functions (which are in vendor.js)

In dashboard.html: Example of how to use transactions related functions
In my_products.html : Example of how to use products related functions
In my_account.html : Example of how to use Account related functions
In index.html : Example of how to initialize some variables
  - server_ip
  - shop_id
  - user_id


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

QRCode Generator for Hello WOrld : <img src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?data=HelloWorld&amp;size=300x300" alt="" title="" />

